snippet.title: Kohan: Immortal Sovereigns Campaign, Mission 2
snippet.description:
Second mission of Kohan: Immortal Sovereigns Campaign. I'm intent on showing everything there's to see in each level but getting them over with quite quickly.

No voice commentary, but I might add subtitles that give some key information in an unintrusive way. And if you want to know something about the game, feel free to comment.
